@base = {{host}}/api
@token = {{token}}

### 1) 点赞成功（预期 HTTP 200，code=0）
POST {{base}}/like/do
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "targetType": "POST",
  "targetId": 1
}

### 2) 重复点赞（预期 HTTP 409，code=411）
POST {{base}}/like/do
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "targetType": "POST",
  "targetId": 1
}

### 3) 取消点赞成功（预期 HTTP 200，code=0）
POST {{base}}/like/undo
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "targetType": "POST",
  "targetId": 1
}

### 4) 重复取消点赞（预期 HTTP 422，code=422）
POST {{base}}/like/undo
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "targetType": "POST",
  "targetId": 1
}

### 5) 未登录点赞（预期 HTTP 401，code=406）
POST {{base}}/like/do
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetType": "POST",
  "targetId": 1
}

### 6) 帖子目标不存在（预期 HTTP 404，code=409）
POST {{base}}/like/do
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "targetType": "POST",
  "targetId": 999999
}

### 7) 评论点赞目标不存在（预期 HTTP 404，code=410）
POST {{base}}/like/do
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "targetType": "COMMENT",
  "targetId": 999999
}

### 8) 评论取消点赞目标不存在（预期 HTTP 404，code=410）
POST {{base}}/like/undo
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "targetType": "COMMENT",
  "targetId": 999999
}

